ROUTINES.createTableSQL:
CREATE TABLE information_schema.ROUTINES (
	SPECIFIC_NAME varchar(192),
	ROUTINE_CATALOG varchar(192),
	ROUTINE_SCHEMA varchar(192),
	ROUTINE_NAME varchar(192),
	ROUTINE_TYPE varchar(27),
	DATA_TYPE varchar(1024),
	CHARACTER_MAXIMUM_LENGTH  bigint(21),
	CHARACTER_OCTET_LENGTH bigint(21),
	NUMERIC_PRECISION bigint(3),
	NUMERIC_SCALE bigint(3),
	DATETIME_PRECISION bigint(3),
	CHARACTER_SET_NAME varchar(12),
	COLLATION_NAME varchar(12),
	DTD_IDENTIFIER varchar(255),
	ROUTINE_BODY varchar(255),
	ROUTINE_DEFINITION varchar(255),
	EXTERNAL_NAME varchar(255),
	EXTERNAL_LANGUAGE varchar(255),
	PARAMETER_STYLE varchar(255),
	IS_DETERMINISTIC varchar(255),
	SQL_DATA_ACCESS char(64),
	SQL_PATH varchar(255),
	SECURITY_TYPE varchar(255),
	CREATED datetime,
	LAST_ALTERED datetime,
	SQL_MODE varchar(80),
	ROUTINE_COMMENT varchar(12),
	DEFINER varchar(64),
	CHARACTER_SET_CLIENT varchar(64),
	COLLATION_CONNECTION varchar(64),
	DATABASE_COLLATION varchar(64)
)

PARAMETERS.createTableSQL:
CREATE TABLE information_schema.parameters (
	SPECIFIC_CATALOG varchar(64),
	SPECIFIC_SCHEMA varchar(64),
	SPECIFIC_NAME varchar(64),
	ORDINAL_POSITION bigint(11) UNSIGNED,
	PARAMETER_MODE varchar(5),
	PARAMETER_NAME varchar(64),
	DATA_TYPE longtext,
	CHARACTER_MAXIMUM_LENGTH bigint(21),
	CHARACTER_OCTET_LENGTH bigint(21),
	NUMERIC_PRECISION int(10) UNSIGNED,
	NUMERIC_SCALE bigint(11),
	DATETIME_PRECISION int(10),
	CHARACTER_SET_NAME varchar(64),
	COLLATION_NAME varchar(64),
	DTD_IDENTIFIER mediumtext,
	ROUTINE_TYPE enum('FUNCTION', 'PROCEDURE')
)
